General.Name: Wirtek A/S
General.Description: Wirtek A/S, an IT outsourcing company, provides software solutions and electronic equipment products in Denmark. It offers software engineering services, including product engineering, system architecture and design, software development, quality assurance, and product re-engineering services; and electronic equipment services that builds, tests, and integrates embedded systems and devices. The company was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Aalborg, Denmark.
